                                            <p class="bn-arbitrator-role">Corporate Arbitrator</p>
                                            <p class="bn-arbitrator-location"><i class="fa fa-map-marker" aria-hidden="true"/> Gurugram</p>
                                            <p class="bn-arbitrator-bio">Handles arbitration involving shareholder, contractual, and corporate governance disputes. He emphasizes confidentiality, efficiency, and commercially sustainable outcomes.</p>
                                        </div>
                                    </article>
                                </div>
