                                            <p class="bn-arbitrator-role">Technology &amp; ODR Arbitrator</p>
                                            <p class="bn-arbitrator-location"><i class="fa fa-map-marker" aria-hidden="true"/> Delhi</p>
                                            <p class="bn-arbitrator-bio">Specializes in arbitration involving cyber law, technology contracts, and digital commerce. A strong advocate of Online Dispute Resolution for fast and secure conflict management.</p>
                                        </div>
                                    </article>
                                </div>
                                <div class="col-sm-6 col-lg-4">
                                    <article class="bn-arbitrator-card">
                                        <div class="bn-arbitrator-photo-wrap">
                                            <div class="bn-arbitrator-photo bn-arbitrator-photo--initials" aria-hidden="true">
                                                <span>HC</span>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="bn-arbitrator-body">
